review.practice_name: The Dental House - Centre For Advanced Dentistry

survey_response.review_text:
Doctor Devang explained each step of the procedure in detail. Since there were two procedures to be carried out on the same day, a dental implant and wisdom tooth extraction, the overall procedure took about an hour. He was considerate of the inconvenience I might feel during the procedures. Hence, instead of rushing through the procedure, he let me take breaks in between while patiently waiting for me to signal him to resume. 
And of course, the entire procedure was painless despite being complicated one.

review.practice_name: The Dental House - Centre For Advanced Dentistry

survey_response.review_text: Doctors at The Dental House are very friendly, ****** ******* and give patients the right guidance. Doctors don't unnecessarily advice for expensive treatment options, rather suggest the most cost effective solution to the dental issues. I got my RCT, Tooth extraction, scaling etc done and am very happy with the treatment outcome all the time. ****** ******* doctors ensured painless experience and quick healing as well.

I didn't have to wait anytime for my check-up as per appointment. I find him very proficient in his dentistry, communication and management skills. He spent sufficient time explaining the dos and don'ts as per my current habits. I felt pretty comfortable as I was worried/ scared of hardcore dentist tools. Overall I would recommend him for his skills, hygienic, updated and we'll maintained clinic.

Dr. Devang diagnosed my pain to my wisdom tooth and within one sitting he extracted two of the wisdom tooths so easily, I am more than satisfied with his expert diagnosis and timely treatment. All in all a delightful experience with a dentist which is very rare.

I found Dr Devang to be a committed professional who is extremely passionate about his work. His constant drive to achieve excellence in his work is admirable. Given the capabilities he possess, I am more than confident that he will rise to become the best in his profession. 
While I recommend him to all, I also wish him success always.
